title: NutriBullet: Peanut Butter Banana Smoothie Bowl Recipe
description:
We're bring peanut butter and banana together in a delicious and filling Blast that's not only perfect for breakfast, but is totally customizable to your tastes. Pour your Blast into a bowl and top with your favorite additions. 

RECIPE:

1  Handful Spinach
1  Bananas
½ Cup Oats
1  Tablespoon Peanut Butter, all natural
1  Tablespoon SuperFood Protein Blend
¼  Teaspoon Cinnamon
1 ½ Cups Almond Milk

1. Add all ingredients to your Tall Cup and extract for 30 seconds, or until smooth.

2. Pour into a bowl and top with your favorite toppings. Options include peanuts, walnuts, oats, cinnamon, banana slices, coconut flakes, chia seeds, and more.
